profile:
ALOMA Home Staging & Design is a full service home staging and design company that values each and every relationship.  Whether you are selling your home or staying, we provide home staging and interior design services that will meet and exceed your expectations. We understand that designing your home, or preparing your property for sale, can seem overwhelming. Not to worry!
We can manage the entire process from start to finish.  We offer a broad range of services for all your staging and design needs.  Serving Ottawa and surrounding areas as well as Prescott-Russell.  Visit our website www.alomahsd.com and contact us!!
